data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT SI.SalesInvoiceId, SI.SaleDate, C.CustomerName, C.PhoneNumber AS CustomerPhone, SI.TotalAmount AS TotalPriceInvoice, SI.Remainder, SI.PaidUp, SI.TotalDiscount, B.BranchName, U.UserName, B.BranchLogo, SI.TotalAmount + SI.TotalDiscount AS TotalBeforeDiscount FROM SalesInvoices SI INNER JOIN Customers C ON SI.CustomerId = C.CustomerId INNER JOIN Branches B ON SI.BranchId = B.BranchId INNER JOIN Users U ON SI.UserId = U.UserId WHERE SI.SalesInvoiceId = @InvoiceId;

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: SELECT SI.ProductId, P.ProductName, CONCAT(S.SizeName, ' ', Col.ColorName) AS dispcrtion, Col.ColorName, SI.Quantity, SI.SellPrice AS SellPricePerItem, SI.SellPrice * SI.Quantity AS TotalSellPrice, SI.ItemDiscount FROM SalesInvoiceItems SII INNER JOIN SalesItems SI ON SII.SalesItemId = SI.SalesItemId INNER JOIN Products P ON SI.ProductId = P.ProductId LEFT JOIN Sizes S ON SI.SizeId = S.SizeId LEFT JOIN Colors Col ON SI.ColorId = Col.ColorId WHERE SII.SalesInvoiceId = @InvoiceId;
